These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
House: craftsman, colonial
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| House   | craftsman | colonial |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Birthday   | june | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different pets are kept: rat, goat
1. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Pet   | goat | rat |

 #################################

 
